{"tid":398702,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有時真係幾配服 點解咁Q多人一齊堆上電梯都唔會出事","createTime":"2017-09-13T11:30:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-13T12:36:53.000Z","uid":63626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"11851e2affb692b241e0e793955768dc408d8b9e","tid":398702,"uid":63626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T11:30:00.000Z","msg":"平時繁忙時間個陣 mtr月台個電梯永遠都會有好撚多人一次過擁埋去<br />\n雖然入口個位係會好撚亂, d人會堆埋一齊行/有人會打尖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過最後都會好順利咁上哂電梯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其間亦無暴力/口角事件發生 每日如是<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n除左有班仆街企左邊又唔行上去之外<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，基本上都無乜大問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n小弟比較少外出旅遊 想知係唔係大部分國家都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n強國情況又是如何<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81adc3813512fbea7695e807c2a052a4fe482b32","tid":398702,"uid":24641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T11:32:39.000Z","msg":"個個都撳緊手機邊得閒互屌"},{"pid":"dce9e426b1236437cc4287f55e7d710c85c0a6a3","tid":398702,"uid":112376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T12:36:53.000Z","msg":"就好似揸車入紅隧咁，個個一出收費站就亂插一通，到最後咪都係一架跟一架入到隧道"}]}